modName: aMidianBorn Differently Ebony Patches - Open Faced Helmet - Dual Sheath Redux SoB - UNPish Female Armor
summary:
This is three different patchs for users of [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/37487//?]Modd3r and CaBaL\'s aMidianBorn Ebony[/url].  
aMidianBorn Differently Ebony Open-Faced Helmets Patch
aMidianBorn Differently Ebony Dual Sheath Redux SoB Patch
aMidianBorn Differently Ebony UNPish Female Armor Patch
descriptionHtml:
This is three different patchs for users of [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/37487//?]Modd3r and CaBaL\'s aMidianBorn Ebony[/url].  

[img]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/37766-1-1372566033.jpg[/img]
aMidianBorn Differently Ebony Open-Faced Helmets Patch - This is made from the open faced ebony helmet mesh made by MadCat221 [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/4866/?]Open Faced Helmets by MadCat221[/url]
---This replaces
---Data\\\\Differently Ebony.esp
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebonyblack\\\\f\\\\helmet_0.nif
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebonyblack\\\\f\\\\helmet_1.nif
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebonyblack\\\\m\\\\helmet_0.nif
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebonyblack\\\\m\\\\helmet_1.nif
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebonygolden\\\\f\\\\helmet_0.nif
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebonygolden\\\\f\\\\helmet_1.nif
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebonygolden\\\\m\\\\helmet_0.nif
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebonygolden\\\\m\\\\helmet_1.nif

[img]http://static.skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/37766-2-1372566034.jpg[/img]
aMidianBorn Differently Ebony Dual Sheath Redux SoB Patch - This is made from the ebony shield on back meshes made by Neovalen [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/34155/?]Dual Sheath Redux by Neovalen[/url]
---This adds
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebonyblack\\\\EbonyShieldOnBack.nif
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebonyblack\\\\EbonyShieldOnBackClk.nif
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebonygolden\\\\EbonyShieldOnBack.nif
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebonygolden\\\\EbonyShieldOnBackClk.nif

[img]http://static.skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/37766-3-1372566034.jpg[/img]
aMidianBorn Differently Ebony UNPish Female Armor Patch - This is made from the female ebony armor mesh made by Sader325 and Shodan44 [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/9109/?]Divine Aegis HD - Paladin Style Ebony Armor Rehaul by Sader and Shodan44[/url]
---This replaces
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebony\\\\f\\\\cuirass_0.nif
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebony\\\\f\\\\cuirass_1.nif
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebonyblack\\\\f\\\\cuirass_0.nif
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebonyblack\\\\f\\\\cuirass_1.nif
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebonygolden\\\\f\\\\cuirass_0.nif
---Data\\\\meshes\\\\armor\\\\ebonygolden\\\\f\\\\cuirass_1.nif

Installation:
Using NMM choose yes when prompted to overwrite.
author: Modd3r - CaBaL - MadCat221 - Neovalen - Sader325 - Shodan44 - Gambit77
